mindmap.markdownDescription:
 Customize the image upload interface. If not filled in, local files will be used by default. 

 For example http://www.api.cn/upload 

 Interface return reference: 

 ```js  
{
    "errno": "0",
    "msg": "ok",
    "data":  {  "url": "http://www.api.cn/public/xxx.png"   } 
}
 ```
